oai_dc:dc.dc:title: LAKE NYASA PORTUGUESE COAST AND ITS SEDIMENTS
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Pacheco, Joao T.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Lake Nyasa
lake sediment
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: On the course of geological work in the Lake Nyasa region, several observations were made on coastal features and beach sediments which allowed some preliminary conclusions to be drawn on sedimentary and coastal processes active in the lake shore. The purpose of this paper is to present these conclusions together with the data on which they are based.
oai_dc:dc.dc:source: Coastal Engineering Proceedings; No. 9 (1964): Proceedings of 9th Conference on Coastal Engineering, Lisbon, Portugal, 1964.; 53
